== Bugs ==
- Transforming a selection causes an extra undo where the selection is gone.
- Select is misaligned to pixels slightly.
- Tabs keep focus when clicking on the canvas and steal arrow key events.

== Features ==
- Change cursor for tool.
- Crop to content command.
- Crop to selection command.
- Show palette path and explain format.
- Example palette.
- Custom shortcuts.
- Use system clipboard for images.
- Allow more zooming out.
- Adjust default zoom size depending on image size when opening.

== Engine ==
- Unit tests for all tools.
- Use commands for canvas operations instead of calling Main.
- Use built in UndoRedo object for undos. 

